    • Method Detail

      • free

        void free()
        Free the chapter. Do NOT use this method for chapters you have not allocated or chapters accessible from a format context. Be really carefull if you have more than one chapter wrapper instances pointing at the same native memory.

      • getId

        int getId()
        Get chapter unique ID. WARNING: The returned value may be cached. Call the clearWrapperCahce() if you think the value have been changed.
        Returns:
        chapter unique ID
